<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <!-- Banner styles moved to partials/header.ejs -->
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <!-- KaTeX for LaTeX rendering -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.9/dist/katex.min.css">
    <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.9/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
    <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.9/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"
      onload="renderMathInElement(document.body, {delimiters: [
        {left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
        {left: '$', right: '$', display: false},
        {left: '\\(', right: '\\)', display: false},
        {left: '\\[', right: '\\]', display: true}
      ]});"></script>
    <style>
      
        .dashboard-links {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 0rem;
          margin-top: 3rem;
          margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        .dashboard-link {
          margin: 0.5rem auto;
          width: 90vw;
          max-width: 700px;
          background: var(--tn-bg, #98a2ce);
          border-radius: 12px;
          padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
          text-align: center;
          font-size: 1.3rem;
          font-weight: bold;
          text-decoration: none;
          color: #24283b;
          box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
          transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
      .dashboard-link:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      }
      .dashboard-link:nth-child(1):hover {
        background: var(--tn-blue, #7aa2f7); /* blue for Overview */
        color: var(--tn-black, #222);
      }
      .dashboard-link:nth-child(2):hover {
        background: var(--tn-green, #9ece6a); /* green for Browse Data */
        color: var(--tn-black, #222);
      }
      .dashboard-link:nth-child(3):hover {
        background: var(--tn-magenta, #bb9af7); /* magenta for Analyze */
        color: var(--tn-black, #222);
      }
      .dashboard-link:nth-child(4):hover {
        background: var(--tn-yellow, #e0af68); /* yellow/orange for Contribute */
        color: var(--tn-black, #3b4261);
      }
      .summary {
        margin: 0.5rem auto;
        width: 90vw;
        max-width: 700px;
        background: var(--tn-bg, #a9b1d6);
        color: var(--tn-black, #3b4261);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.0rem 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <p>Interface for organizing and accessing high-throughput computational screening data from research studies.</p>
    
    <div class="dashboard-links">
      <a class="dashboard-link" href="/overview">Overview<br><span style="font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:normal;">Research details, infrastructure, parameters</span></a>
      <a class="dashboard-link" href="/browse">Browse<br><span style="font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:normal;">Explore all host materials and data</span></a>
      <a class="dashboard-link" href="/analyze">Analyze<br><span style="font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:normal;">Query and visualize selected data</span></a>
      <a class="dashboard-link" href="/contribute">Contribute<br><span style="font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:normal;">Request to add your data</span></a>
    </div>
    <div class="summary">
      <h2>About</h2>
      <p>This web application provides tools for managing, browsing, analyzing, and contributing to a large collection of computational screening data. The structure and features are designed to be extensible and adaptable to evolving research needs.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>~10 host crystal families</li>
        <li>Hundreds of unique point defects per family</li>
        <li>Data organized by screening workflow stages</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
